OK, this is my second map now and it is my first release
at "Under The Gun" studio. It's got skybox and proper
lighting, added nodraw to every point of the map i could for best fps.
It's has cubemaps and a little bit of wind to make it a bit more realistic.
Textures are standard but look great in my opinion, tried to add HDR
but it turned guns a funny green colour plus it was just to bright!
Anyway this is just the start of mapping for me and will be making
more maps of every kind in the near future.

I made this map from scratch and did NOT remake fy_poolparty!
I made a nav aswell because i see alot of people bitchin
about maps without nav's(o.0)
